PLACEHOLDER

Drop your professional headshot here, named profile.jpg.

Recommendations (see design_system/design_tokens.md):
- ~600px wide minimum
- Shoulders-up, face in upper half
- Neutral background
- JPEG quality 85-90
- Target size: 80-150 KB

The HTML references this image as ../_shared/profile.jpg, so once
you save it with the right filename in this folder, every variant
renders with your photo automatically.

Delete this placeholder file once your real profile.jpg is in place.
